Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:03.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From a different perspective...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.19,0:00:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An imposing wall is just a large door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The red "shadow" left behind at the scene, unfolding according to the plot of a novel...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mysterious unseen suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:11.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:52.65,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Sasamoto Yasutarou (32)\NCompany Employee
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.79,0:02:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:08.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.79,0:02:09.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shadow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikage...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:29.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's Kamio...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:32.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Sasamoto—are you still sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was up with Sensei all night...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:36.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't get home until dawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikage...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikage appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:42.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you ambushed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm heading to the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll head there too—don't leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take a taxi and be there in 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:49.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:03:00.13,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Kamio Toshiyuki (32)\NMystery Magazine Editor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:05.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just as you predicted...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:06.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamio...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But will they believe us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:13.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can ask a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were almost killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:20.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:22.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We already know the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was a member of our mystery investigation club in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man called Hikage Taeichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:32.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What makes you so sure he's the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:33.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Half a month ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I received a script sent by Hikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Script?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:39.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For a novel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying that he will kill all of his old partners, one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a murder prophecy novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:47.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Murder prophecy novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:55.31,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,AND IT'D BE NICE IF EVERYBODY DISAPPEARED
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would've been bad if you had been hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could definitely kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:05.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But using red paint to write the words...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's got some vulgar tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:10.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been like that since our college days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even the novel he wrote on a computer had a title in bright red letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He always wore sunglasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's definitely Hikage—there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You received the novel from Hikage-san about half a month ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Mystery Investigation Club had 18 members, but only 4 were active.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:33.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those people were...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sasamoto and myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:37.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nesu Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Hikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:43.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've barely seen each other since graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, half a month ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got a script at the mystery magazine company where I work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:55.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For work named "And It'd Be Nice If Everybody Disappeared"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There weren't any mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:00.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There weren't any tricks, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a story of revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where the main character's hatred causes him to kill his three friends from college...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:12.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something other than the content that you won't believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:14.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The names of those three murdered people are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:16.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nesu Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamio Toshiyuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Sasamoto Yasutaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, our names!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I finally figured out the meaning of this strange novel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:26.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two days ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two nights ago, at Beika Park...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:33.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone discovered a male corpse that had been impaled by a dagger...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:39.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim was one of our members, Nesu Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:43.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the novel sent by Hikage...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nesu Takeshi... was murdered in a park at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you mind letting me take a look at the novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:55.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder method is the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means this isn't a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's certainly not a coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:04.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This novel is a murder prophecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:06.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But something's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though he specified the murder method for Nesu Takeshi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murders of both Sasamoto-san and Kamio-san are not explained in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:18.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:22.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:25.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When and where does he plan to kill us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The motive for murder seems to be the hatred caused by everyone's harsh criticisms of the novel he wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:36.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, there was an incident like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The setting process no longer works.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trick isn't inventive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are no surprising twists in the plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:50.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The emotions are too dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:52.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means that there's no basic reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's not like that never happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamio, your novel was criticized by Hikage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:02.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's so interesting about your novel, Kamio?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was my most confident work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You need a smack on the head to wake that brain up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This kind of crap can't pass for a story at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone was the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been 10 years—why seek revenge after all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Hikage-san recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:22.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We thought that he was already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:30.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:34.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikage left home three years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that he was going to the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:38.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, he never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:42.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why everyone thought that he died in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that guy is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man who has been presumed dead for three years...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Setting his plan for revenge into action after all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:53.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamio-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a package for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Package?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it royalties for your script?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never turn in any scripts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:07.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:09.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, don't open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, that was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:24.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got pretty lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:26.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that there wasn't enough gunpowder...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he miscalculated how much he needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:31.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've determined that it was sent by Hikage Taeichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:39.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The package had this inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:42.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's definitely Hikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's another thing that the public hasn't yet been made aware of...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found the same thing under the corpse of Nasu Takeshi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamio-san, you should remain inside the hospital for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll be protecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:02.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your work can be done from the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your head editor has already agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:08.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sasamoto-san is a salesman...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That won't work for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri-san and I will protect you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:17.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:18.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go home immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:27.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:32.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to figure out Hikage Taeichi's whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be best to find his hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I cannot leave here no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:45.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:47.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:48.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:50.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My waist...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:55.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:09:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:01.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikage...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Hikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You won't be hurt while we're around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bomb failed, so he tried a hit-and-run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:22.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That car hit the brakes when it rushed through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bomb sent to Kamio-san didn't have enough gunpowder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it supposed to be a threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nesu Takeshi-san was actually murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:43.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nesu-san, Kamio-san, and Sasamoto-san were all handled differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is there no consistency in the culprit's actions?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:49.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:52.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:58.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was unfortunate that I didn't catch that car yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next time he appears, I will definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:04.28,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,CALLING
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:05.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:07.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Hikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you're under the protection of the police and a detective, you don't need to worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:16.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll let you go this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:18.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's retreating?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:21.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, I will not give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:23.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will definitely kill you if there is an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, Hikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:26.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:28.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamio-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikage just called.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:33.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He called me too. /
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He seems to be giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can finally relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we can't just let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikage Taeichi committed a crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:46.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to catch him no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:51.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They weren't able to find Hikage Taeichi's hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:07.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After his disappearance three years ago, he didn't contact anyone around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:14.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He should've at least written about his hideout in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If past hatred is the motive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:19.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There may be clues in the novels he wrote in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.23,0:12:21.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Novels from college...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are they still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:26.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a magazine at my house...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:28.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was issued by the members of the Mystery Investigation Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:33.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anything in that magazine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't any clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:39.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:44.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This style of writing is like...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:50.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:53.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's his purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:12:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This seems like a wasted trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably intended for us to drop our guard as a result of that phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:13.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we don't catch Hikage Taeichi soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to Sensei's place today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:21.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Detective Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:26.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of person was the deceased Nesu Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now's not the time to talk about that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:33.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His reputation wasn't very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:37.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One person was angry at him because he never paid a debt that he owed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:38.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Money...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:42.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nesu did?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:44.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asked me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:44.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he ask you anything about money?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:49.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He claimed he would get the money, but it was still suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he'd use the incident from three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:13:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it the disappearance of Hikage-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikage-san was a very hard-working person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he wanted to become a famous writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He worked toward that goal every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I guess he failed in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Failed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:16.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was two or three days before he left...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:20.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He burned the novel he wrote in the backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He burned it and cried in front of his friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:23.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:28.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he among these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This person...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you burning this masterpiece?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person said it was awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:41.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that it had absolutely no value.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've wasted seven years working on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:48.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shortly after that, he disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I think that's why he went to the mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:54.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to commit his suicide in despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:55.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:02.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was me who called everyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:02.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said that you solved all the mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:06.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mystery in this case is far from—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:16.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It started already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleeping Kogorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:21.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Feelings of hatred, stemming from college...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is the true motive behind all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:26.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've known that the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:31.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was stated in the novel that the culprit, Hikage Taeichi, wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case has nothing to do with Hikage-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has nothing to do with...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that, Mouri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:44.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikage-san wanted to become a famous writer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:49.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trying to realize his dream, he worked hard writing mystery novels even after graduating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We already knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, he was stressed because he couldn't write any satisfactory works.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:16:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Hikage-san finally finished a masterpiece three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:03.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, regarding that piece of work...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:09.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikage-san took it to his past partner, who is now an editor of a mystery magazine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamio-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He brought it to your place, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:16.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this true, Kamio?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After reading it, you immediately realized that it was a true masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:24.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:26.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Kamio?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is really awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably did this because your confident work from your college years had been rejected by Hikage-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:47.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a result, he believed your words and committed suicide in his despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:48.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're being attacked by Hikage right now, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:53.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:57.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Hikage-san disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamio-san was already aware...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:04.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That it was because he planned to commit suicide out of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:09.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must have felt guilty for your actions three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the same time, you tried very hard to forget that incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, half a month ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your past partner, Nesu Takeshi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:20.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Started to blackmail you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikage died three years ago because of you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did I guess right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:30.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He also showed me his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In truth, I really need money right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To you, money probably wasn't the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:46.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you couldn't sit with the fact that someone else knew of the painful past you wanted to forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a result, you decided to eliminate Nesu Takeshi-san from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if you killed him straightforwardly, you would become a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:57.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you made up a culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:18:00.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Making it seem like Hikage Taeichi-san had committed the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You crafted the scenario to make the motive appear to be hatred out of slandered work from college.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, Nesu-san was not the only one who criticized Hikage-san's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Sasamoto-san and yourself weren't being targeted as well, then it would be suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to make people believe that Hikage-san was trying to exact his revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:27.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wrote the novel, "And It'd Be Nice If Everybody Disappeared."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you really write that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:32.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, in the park...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:35.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You killed Nesu-san as illustrated in the novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You also disguised as Hikage-san and ambushed Sasamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikage appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:43.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll head there too—don't leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:46.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take a taxi and be there in 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You pretended as if you had answered the phone at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:50.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, 30 minutes later...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:54.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You acted as though you had just rushed from your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:59.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then led us to believe that you were being targeted by Hikage-san as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You also found an opportunity to sneak out of the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:08.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You disguised as Hikage-san and targeted Sasamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you used his voice to deceive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:12.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Hikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:18.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we think about it this way, we can understand why the culprit's actions lack consistency.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only one you wanted to kill from the beginning was Nesu Takeshi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:26.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I right, Kamio-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't these just deductions?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri-san, you don't have any proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sasamoto-san still remembers...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The company of the taxi that you rode in yesterday morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:46.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The taxi driver will probably remember that there was a strange customer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who got off near the crime scene after riding only 800 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You call that a testimony?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:56.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible that he could have mixed you up with someone else, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not the only piece of evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:00.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This man...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:01.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:03.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This thing won't wash off no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you were using the red paint...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:10.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably got some on the bottom of your shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamio-san, may we take a look at them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The soles of your shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:21.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamio...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:26.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How and when did you realize I was the culprit, Mouri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That novel...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"And It'd Be Nice If Everybody Disappeared."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I realized that the author couldn't have been Hikage Taeichi-san—it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:40.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It had your writing style.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:42.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Writing style?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The writing style for that novel is different from the novel that Hikage-san wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:56.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikage-san's novel employed much more emotional punctuations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:59.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, there weren't any in that particular novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:05.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In addition, there isn't any punctuation for space; it was directly expressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:08.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a very repressed writing style.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was written in the same style as your past novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:20.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Writing habits are hard to change, no matter how many years have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:24.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially after an author is able to thrive on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:27.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is unavoidable, Kamio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:30.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Humans are animals that cannot change their habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.95,0:21:33.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamio...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.08,0:21:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Animals who cannot change their habits, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gonna go wash my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:31.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Murder prophecy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.03,0:23:31.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In here...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.24,0:23:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The red "shadow!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:35.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.70,0:23:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help me, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.24,0:23:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.12,0:23:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.75,0:23:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that just a trace of your saliva?
